rComments: She is an awesome prof. Best in my academic career spanning 4 degrees. Very approachable and makes sure students understand topics before moving onto others. Very much recommended to take her classes. Provides great feedback and very helpful, makes time for students after class.

rComments: Awesome prof. Makes research interesting!! Really applies research to our practice and provides great case studies to work with. She knows her stuff and is a great teacher. Quite a few assignments, but not difficult. Surprisingly a great class despite my initial annoyance with the thought of research.

She is really energetic.  She will explain things until the entire class understands and she can sense when you don't quite get things.  She wants assignments to be very thorough but short, so make it concise.
Very helpful and very motivated. She manages to make quantitative research interesting.
